name: Beaded 'Horizon' Cuff
description:
This beaded cuff is part of the JWS Horizon Collection. 
These are available in many colors but this particular cuff is a blend of Blue, Bronze, Beige and Brown seed beads.  Measurement 
1 1/4"W x 7 1/4L.  JWS cuffs have a completely adjustable aluminum base. Denim fabric lining.
